OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy this morning with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, drying up from the
OL,7,Fsouth later. Sunny spells and a few
OL,8,Fshowers this afternoon, these turning
OL,9,Fheavy in the south later. Warm in any
OL,10,Fsunshine.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThis evening will be partly
OL,13,Fcloudy with scattered showers, heavy
OL,14,Fat first. Then the rest of the night
OL,15,Fwill see variable amounts of cloud and
OL,16,Fsome showery rain.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FSome bright or sunny spells
OL,19,Fthrough the day and a scattering of
OL,20,Fshowers, these heavy in the northwest.
OL,21,FBecoming drier through the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
